            called "The Well" that seemed to be an "Elite =
Place".<BR><BR>When=20
            GIF was all Compuserve and users had email names like=20
            "36467354"<BR><BR>and finding my first dialup's that =
connected to=20
            UNIX boxes....<BR><BR>and then Getting TCP/IP over PPP for =
